ZH: 天网恢恢，疏而不漏。
EN: The net of heaven is wide and meshes are tight.

ZH: 天网恢恢，犯错者必受惩罚。
EN: The net of heaven is wide and none shall escape punishment.

ZH: 天网恢恢，有众多证据说明了他的罪行。
EN: The net of heaven is wide and there is ample evidence of his wrongdoing.

ZH: 天网恢恢，任何不法之徒终将落入法网。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, and all criminals will eventually be caught.

ZH: 天网恢恢，百姓永远是最大的受益者。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, and the people will always benefit the most.

ZH: 天网恢恢，不法分子总有一天会受到应有的惩罚。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, and wrongdoers will one day receive their due punishment.

ZH: 天网恢恢，不要抱有侥幸心理。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, do not harbor any delusions of escaping punishment.

ZH: 天网恢恢，无论你藏得再深，也会被揪出来。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, no matter how well you hide, you will be exposed.

ZH: 天网恢恢，罪恶终究难逃。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, and evil will never escape.

ZH: 天网恢恢，只有诚实的人才能安然无恙。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, only the honest can be safe.

ZH: 天网恢恢，无论是犯错还是无辜，都会得到应有的待遇。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, whether guilty or innocent, all will receive their due.

ZH: 天网恢恢，只要你做了坏事，迟早会被揭露出来。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, if you do wrong, it will be revealed sooner or later.

ZH: 天网恢恢，正义终究会得到伸张。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, justice will prevail in the end.

ZH: 天网恢恢，别以为只有自己知道的事情天知地知。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, do not think that what you know is hidden from everyone.

ZH: 天网恢恢，心怀叵测的人终会自食其果。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, those with ulterior motives will eventually reap what they sow.

ZH: 天网恢恢，永远不要背叛自己的良心。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, never betray your own conscience.

ZH: 天网恢恢，不要以为可以逃脱惩罚。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, do not think you can escape punishment.

ZH: 天网恢恢，一切恶行都将被揭露。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, all evil deeds will be exposed.

ZH: 天网恢恢，任何不公正的事情终将得到纠正。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, any injustice will eventually be rectified.

ZH: 天网恢恢，只有正直的人才能在天网下安居乐业。
EN: The net of heaven is wide, only the upright can thrive under its gaze.
